{
  "page": "Green Canal",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Green Canal</b> is one of the larger canals in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Location\">Location</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Canal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Location\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Green Canal is located in eastern Braavos. It leads from the <a href=\"/index.php/Palace_of_Truth\" title=\"Palace of Truth\">Palace of Truth</a> in the city center to the east side of the lagoon in which the hundred isles of Braavos are located. The <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetwater_river\" title=\"Sweetwater river\">sweetwater river</a> crosses the Green Canal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Canal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Braavos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404100829\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 82/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 308/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 50/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 537/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.513      1 -total\n 75.73%    4.175      1 Template:Ref\n 45.69%    2.519      1 Template:Ref/core\n 23.00%    1.268      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:22084-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404100829 and revision id 274964\n -->\n",
